## Socket & Path Constants

Always use the constants from `pluginapi` rather than hard-coding paths:

| Constant                     | Value                                         | Usage                          |
|------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------|--------------------------------|
| `pluginapi.DevicePluginPath` | `/var/lib/kubelet/device-plugins/`             | Directory for plugin sockets   |
| `pluginapi.KubeletSocket`    | `/var/lib/kubelet/device-plugins/kubelet.sock` | Kubelet registration endpoint  |
| `pluginapi.Version`          | `v1beta1`                                      | API version for registration   |

